<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{مهطعين}</span> أَيْ: مُسْرِعِينَ إِلَى <span class="c2">(نَحْوِ)</span> الدَّعْوَةِ <span class="c2">(ل ١٦٧)</span> حِينَ يَدْعُوهُمْ إِلَى بَيْتِ الْمَقْدِسِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ محمدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(مُهْطِعِينَ)</span> منصوبٌ عَلَى الْحَال.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>